description:
NKCL is a personalized immune-care platform using NK cell. NK cell is an effective immunity cell which is well known for the next generation anti-cancer treatment and it is efficient with various diseases and beauty industries such as anti-aging, auto-immune diseases and cell- beauty.
NKCL records all the medical big data such as NK Cell procedure, clinical results, cultivation conditions, and cultivation results that occur during the treatment process in Blockchain and establishes a transparent and secure medical big data trading platform based on recorded medical data.
